sub_title: Research Analyst – Dairy Physics and Chemistry at FrieslandCampina
summary: I'm a broadly oriented Analytical chemist that wants to put the practical skills of the MLO and HLO and my academic mindset into practice. I'm eager to learn new skills, driven and have an attention to detail. I like to brainstorm about new ideas with a team and I’m not afraid to take responsibility and work independently. My ambition is to work in a multidisciplinary environment and to focus on research and development.
